arm_group.description:
Tazemetostat 800 mg BID orally as tablets continuously starting on Day 1, with the exception of the morning dose on Day 16;
A single IV dose of approximately 12 µg tazemetostat that contains approximately 500 nCi of [14C] tazemetostat on Day 15;
A single oral dose of 800 mg tazemetostat as a solution containing approximately 400 µCi (14.8 MBq) of [14C] tazemetostat on Day 16.
